| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5155 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5c4c4167-8c37-57c7-9e4b-1d78fdc6c00c"
